{"id":308846,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/香港獨立媒體-救救南生圍-南生圍-與-香港房屋政策/","date":"2013-08-14T12:36:10Z","modified":"2013-08-14T12:36:10Z","title":"香港獨立媒體 | [救救南生圍] 南生圍 與 香港房屋政策","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n                    <img class=\"imagefield imagefield-field_image\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/969376_10151534244605885_2073288302_n.jpg?1376472828\" />        </div>\n<div>\n                    <img class=\"imagefield imagefield-field_image\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/67778_441527505884_5444938_n.jpg?1376473387\" />        </div>\n<div>\n                    <img class=\"imagefield imagefield-field_image\" width=\"281\" height=\"500\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/561537_10151567006805885_1179349567_n_0.jpg?1376473489\" />        </div>\n<div>\n                    <img class=\"imagefield imagefield-field_image\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/998442_10151567328310885_534805781_n.jpg?1376473510\" />        </div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<p>[救救南生圍]一波未平, 一波又起!<br />\n“新地南生圍申建45幢洋房”<br />\n(城規會申請編號: A/YL-NSW/223)<br />\n請大家到城規會網頁發表意見:<br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_YL-NSW_223.html\" title=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_YL-NSW_223.html\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_YL-NSW_223.html</a><br />\n截止提交意見日期:27/08/2013</p>\n<p>南生圍是筆者愛上生態的發源地!<br />\n筆者第一次親眼見到黑臉琵鷺飛過的地方正是南生圍,<br />\n當時筆者是一位小學五年級學生.</p>\n<p>近日發展商不斷向政府申請在南生圍建豪宅,<br />\n更在計畫書上寫着:<br />\n<strong>&#8220;發展完全符合政府最新的房屋政策, 以增加房屋供應&#8221;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>筆者認為政府的房屋政策是指 增加公屋及居屋供應,<br />\n而並非低密度高價格的房屋.</strong></p>\n<p>希望有更多人向城市規劃委員會(城規會)表達意見,<br />\n勿讓發展商 &#8220;強暴&#8221; 香港的房屋政策!</p>\n<div>\n<div>影像串流: </div>\n<div>\n<div>\n                    <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WiMYq-bTvzE\">See video</a>        </div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>影像串流: </div>\n<div>\n<div>\n                    <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TLKoQn8yLEs\">See video</a>        </div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<p><object type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" data=\"http://youtube.com/v/WiMYq-bTvzE\" width=\"250\" height=\"206\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://youtube.com/v/WiMYq-bTvzE\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/v/WiMYq-bTvzE\">http://youtube.com/v/WiMYq-bTvzE</a></object> </p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196,8712]}